echo "   - To: yield list(row)"

echo "   - Changed: self.OUT = codecs.getwriter('utf-8')(sys.stdout, errors='replace')"
echo "   - To: self.OUT = io.TextIOWrapper(sys.stdout.buffer, encoding='utf-8', errors='replace')"
echo "   - Reason: codecs.getwriter() requires a binary stream in Python 3"
echo ""
echo "3. CSV reading:"
echo "   - Changed: header_labels = list(csvreader.next())"
echo "   - To: header_labels = list(next(csvreader))"
echo "   - Reason: csvreader.next() is deprecated in Python 3"
echo ""
echo "4. Error handling:"
echo "   - Changed: e.message"
echo "   - To: str(e)"
echo "   - Reason: Python 3 exceptions don't have 'message' attribute"
echo ""
echo "5. ConfigParser:"
echo "   - Changed: config.readfp(open(opts['-f']))"
echo "   - To: config.read_file(open(opts['-f']))"
echo "   - Reason: readfp() is deprecated and removed in Python 3.12"
